<%- include('partials/header') %>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Text and Single Image Layout</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            width: 90%;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .text-section {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .text-section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .text-section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #666;
        }
        .image-section {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .image-section img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        /* Mobile-friendly styling */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .text-section, .image-section {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .text-section h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .text-section p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            .image-section img {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-section">
            <h2>Modern Kitchen</h2>
            <p>Step into a sleek and functional space where minimalist aesthetics meet high-end functionality. Stainless steel appliances blend seamlessly with polished marble countertops, while open shelving and hidden cabinets maximize storage and style.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="/images/img/kitchen.jpg" alt="Modern Kitchen">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-section">
            <h2>Luxury Living Room</h2>
            <p>Designed for both comfort and elegance, this living room is a sanctuary of refined taste. A neutral color palette allows for bold accent pieces, while plush seating invites relaxation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="/images/img/1 (10).jpg" alt="Luxury Living Room">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-section">
            <h2>Scandinavian Bedroom</h2>
            <p>Embrace simplicity and warmth with Scandinavian design, where natural light floods the space and every element serves a purpose. Clean lines and wooden accents create a peaceful retreat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="/images/img/1 (31).jpg" alt="Scandinavian Bedroom">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-section">
            <h2>Minimalist Office</h2>
            <p>This modern workspace is a masterpiece of minimalism, featuring clean lines, neutral tones, and carefully curated furniture that promotes focus and productivity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="/images/img/office.jpg" alt="Minimalist Office">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-section">
            <h2>Elegant Dining Room</h2>
            <p>The dining room offers a perfect blend of tradition and modernity, with a grand table as its centerpiece. A chandelier casts a warm glow over stylish seating, while carefully chosen d√©cor elements add a touch of opulence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="/images/img/dining.jpg" alt="Elegant Dining Room">
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

